<P><center><font color="red">Wishing you a safe and <BR>Happy Holiday Season!</font>
<P>Northeast Utilities is an electric utility holding company that 

serves about 1.7 million customers through its operating subsidiaries

in Connecticut, western Massachusetts and New Hampshire.  It is New England's 

largest electric utility system and one  of the 20 largest in the United States of 

America.



